  "about": {
    "body": [
      "I'm a 32-year-old designer from Pärnu, Estonia, currently based in Helsinki, Finland. I enjoy playing and making video games, visiting museums, travelling and cooking.",
      "I'm a product-minded design generalist. I've shaped B2B software, service platforms, and most recently video game UI and interaction systems. I care about making complex things feel simple and intuitive, without sacrificing personality.",
      "My work spans UX, UI, interaction design, and visual design. I like understanding the full stack of a product, from wireframes to motion to front-end, so I can design with real constraints in mind.",
      "I prefer working in-house where I can go deep on a product, but I'm open to the right freelance collaboration. If you think we'd work well together — let's talk."
    ],
